text: Phrynetopsis loveni is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1925. It was described by Tanzania, Kenya, and Uganda.BioLib.cz - Phrynetopsis loveni. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1925
